            <ol>
                <li class="obj p-3">To properly implement the University Research Agenda;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">To dramatically improve the research capabilities and skills of the University's faculty and employees;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">To exponentially increase the CHED-recognized / ISI / Scopus-indexed research presentation and publications of all faculty and employees in all campuses and branches of the University;</li>
