            <div class="flex-grow-1 border-bottom mb-1"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-0 p-3 me-5 ms-5">
            <p class="justp">The Research Management Office (RMO), a leading arm for research production, administration, dissemination, publication, and utilization under the Office of the Vice President for Research, Extension, and Development (OVPRED), adopts this official logo to represent its core functions in accordance to the University's vision, mission, and objectives.</p>
        </div>

