            <div class="flex-grow-1 border-bottom"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-0 p-3 me-5 ms-5">
            <p class="justp">To symbolize the vision, mission, and core functions of the Research Management Office (RMO), the logo contains the following elements and their corresponding meaning:</p>
            <ol>
                <li class="obj p-3">Book:  Scientific knowledge generation and education;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">Tree: University research culture enhancement;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">Lightbulb: Creative thinking and innovation;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">Gear: Engine for research progress and internationalization;</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">Golden Leaves: Research rewards and awards; and</li>
                <li class="obj p-3">People: Internal and external linkages with stakeholders.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
